# Proyek: Website Remaja Masjid Istiqomah (RMI)

## Struktur Monorepo

```
rmi/
├── frontend/          # Next.js 14, App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind
├── backend/           # Express.js + MongoDB (Sprint 20+)
├── docs/prd/          # Product Requirements (terpisah per topik)
├── docs/roadmap/      # 43 sprint guide — sumber kebenaran urutan kerja
└── project.md         # Brief awal
```

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Teknologi |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | Next.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind, TanStack Query, Axios, RHF, Zod, Framer Motion |
| Backend | Node.js, Express, Mongoose, JWT, Cloudinary |
| DB | MongoDB Atlas |

## Pendekatan Development

**Visual First** — frontend + mock data dulu (Sprint 01–19), backend kemudian (20–28), integrasi (29–33), CMS (34–40), launch (41–43).

## Dokumentasi Kunci

| Kebutuhan | File |
|-----------|------|
| Mulai coding | `docs/roadmap/README.md` |
| Sprint aktif | `docs/roadmap/sprint-XX-*.md` |
| Functional reqs | `docs/prd/04-functional-requirements.md` |
| Warna & UX | `docs/prd/06-design-ux.md` |
| Database | `docs/prd/09-database-schema.md` |
| API | `docs/prd/10-api-specification.md` |

## Prinsip Kode

- React functional components + TypeScript
- Komponen reusable di `frontend/src/components/ui/`
- Custom hooks di `frontend/src/hooks/`
- Minimize scope — diff kecil, fokus, jangan over-engineer
- Mobile-first, responsif, aksesibel
